	send-repl-results-to-emacs.

2007-08-28  Matthias Koeppe  <mkoeppe@mail.math.uni-magdeburg.de>

	* swank-presentations.lisp (send-repl-results-to-emacs):
	Override core defun to mark up REPL results as presentations.

